---
title: Mediterranean Roasted Eggplant Trottole with Cherry Tomatoes & Crumbly Cheese
description: Add layers of flavour to trottole with an array of rainbow veggies roasted in Mediterranean-inspired seasonings. Paired with a rich
cherry tomato sauce and aromatic thyme, your finished dish will be transformed into a taste sensation.
